  "original_title": "\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dc3\u0dca\u0dad\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc5\u0dd0\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc0\u0dd3\u0dd3\u0db8\u0dda \u0db4\u0db1\u0dad \u0dba\u0da7\u0dad\u0dda \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d87\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0dc4\u0dcf \u0dba\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db4\u0dba\u0dda \u0d85\u0dc0\u0db0\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The arrest under the Prevention of Terrorism Act is the focus of America and Europe",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The attention of the United States as well as the European Union has been focused on arresting, detaining and questioning under the Prevention of Terrorism Act.",
        "The Ministry of Defense has approved the detention and questioning of three people, including the convener of the Inter-University Student Council, Wasantha Mudalige, for 90 days under the Prevention of Terrorism Act.",
        "Mrs. Julie Chung, the American Ambassador to Sri Lanka, expressed her views on this on her Twitter account.",
        "The use of laws that do not comply with international human rights standards, such as the Prevention of Terrorism Act, erodes Sri Lanka's democracy. We encourage the government to uphold the right of the people to express themselves.",
        "In this regard, the EU representatives in Sri Lanka expressed their views on their Twitter account.",
        "Reports of the use of the Prevention of Terrorism Act in recent arrests are worrying."
      ],
